Package com.mycompany.ui

Class Blackhole

java.lang.Object
com.mycompany.ui.StaticObject
com.mycompany.ui.Blackhole
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collidable
public class Blackhole
extends StaticObject
implements Collidable
This class represents a black hole within outer space aka the factory. It inherits from the StaticObject class and implements the Collidable interface. There is 1 black hole per round.
Author:
jnesis. adapted by stacey
